testsuite.class: Validate that runs can be cancelled using the api.

testcase.class: API_CANCEL_RUN - cancelRun - cancelRun tests Validate that runs can be cancelled using the api. S_Bash_CancelRun_6110_0001 User creates a pipeline with multiple steps and starts a run. User cancels the run while the run is Waiting. The run state moves to cancelled.
